10px) and (max-width: 1199.98px) 100vw, (max-width: 809.98px) 100vw"></div><div style="flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px"><div style="display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:8px"><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-weight:700;font-family:&quot;Inter&quot;, &quot;Inter Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3em">Laura (Atlagrid)</span><span style="color:rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);font-family:&quot;Inter&quot;, &quot;Inter Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:12px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.3em">12:30 PM</span></div><div style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height:1.46em;word-break:break-word;font-family:&quot;Inter&quot;, &quot;Inter Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:15px;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em">I chose Latitud over YC because they're new and have everything to prove. That meant they'd fight harder for us—and they did.</div><div style="display:flex;gap:4px;margin-top:4px;flex-wrap:wrap"><button style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:8px 12px;background-color:rgb(3, 33, 38);border:1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);border-radius:99px;cursor:pointer;transition:background-color 0.1s ease, border-color 0.1s ease;font-family:&quot;Inter&quot;, &quot;Inter Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-style:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1em"><span style="font-size:11px">🫡</span><span style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255);font-size:11px;font-weight:400">3</span></button><button style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:4px;padding:8px 12px;background-color:rgb(3, 33, 38);border:1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);border-radius:99px;cursor:pointer;transition:background-color 0.1s ease, border-color 0.1s ease;font-family:&quot;Inter&quot;, &quot;Inter Placeholder&quot;, sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-style:normal;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1em"><s